headline: NRL 2022: As it happened - Manly too good for Newcastle
author: Paul Zalunardo
sentences:
Newcastle
Kalyn Ponga - Looked down and out when assisted from the field late in the first half but came back and never stopped trying.
Daly Cherry-Evans - A cool head who used his kicking skills to their fullest.
Haumole Olakau’atu - Deserved his try after another powerful display.
Kurt Mann - Mr Fix-It will go wherever he’s needed and do a good job.

Manly
Jake Trbojevic - His best 80-minutes of the season.
Bradman Best - Had a great battle with Morgan Harper.
His commitment to the cause could not be questioned.
Looks a real tower of strength out wide.
